      "rationale": "Across all five flow-speed combinations, the CFD-predicted NIH deviates from experimental measurements by a maximum of 11.4% and a mean of 6.8%. All predictions fall within the ±15% acceptance band. Agreement is strongest at mid-range flow rates (3–5 L/min), consistent with the primary COU operating envelope."
